                  (0.1 and 0.5 microg). Neither MK-801 (0.1, 0.5 and 5
                  microg) nor the NMDA receptor agonist, NMDA (0.5 and
                  1 microg), injected unilaterally into the shell,
                  produced turning behaviour. Unilateral injection of
                  a mixture of dopamine D(1) (SKF 38393, 5 microg) and
                  D(2) (quinpirole, 10 microg) receptor agonists into
